\">μ͡ν͡ή\u003C/span>σθητι \u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ\u003C/span>(ύρι)\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ε\u003C/span> ἐν \u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡ῇ\u003C/span> βασιλείᾳ σου \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>Ἐτελειώθησαν μ(ηνὶ) Δεκε\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">μ͡β\u003C/span>ρίῳ κζ´ \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>Ἰν\u003Cspan class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">δ\u003C/span>(ικτιῶνος) ἕκ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">τ͡η\u003C/span>ς´ ⸙ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>+ΤΥ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Β͡Ο͡Σ\u003C/span>ΕΝ\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Θ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ω\u003C/span>ΚΕΙΜΕΝΩΝΕΝΘΑΔΕΕΝΑΝΑΠΑΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>ΣΕΙΚΩΝΣΤΑΝΤΙΝ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ο͡Υ\u003C/span>ΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΣΕ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η\u003C/span>ΙΒΜΕΛΛΩ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>Σ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ο͡Υ\u003C/span>ΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΣΕ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η\u003C/span>ΙΚΝΙΚΗΤΑΖΗΣΑΝΤΟΣΕ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η\u003C/span>Η\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΤΟΥΤΩΝ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Ν͡Η\u003C/span>ΣΘΗΤΙ\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ε\u003C/span>ΕΝ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η\u003C/span>ΒΑΣΙΛΕΙΑΣΟΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΕΤΕΛΕΙΩΘΗΣΑΝΜΔΕΚΕ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Β\u003C/span>ΡΙΩΚΖ\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ΙΝ\u003Cspan class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">Δ\u003C/span>ΕΚ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η\u003C/span>Σ⸙\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Manganaro 2001, with ligatures added\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Tomb of those lying in God at rest, of Constantine, who lived 12 years, of Mellosos, who lived 10 years and of Niketas who lived 8 years. Remember these in your kingdom, O Lord! They died in the month of December on the 27th (day), in the 6th Indiction.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Tomba dei giacenti in Dio qui in pace, di Costantino vissuto anni dodici, di Melloso vissuto anni dieci e di Niceta vissuto anni otto. Di questi ricordati, o Signore, nel tuo regno! Morirono nel mese di dicesmbre (il giorno) ventisette. della indizione sesta.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>  \u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 51.1378 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 42.0869 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rocco 1983 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001619\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001619\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 1988-1989 360-361 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002120\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002120\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 2001 131-134 fig.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001807\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001807\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Extensive use of ligatures\u003C/p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[205,208,211,214,217,219,222,225,228],{"id":206,"html":207},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/JVCEV98D\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\