ers are joined\">Τ͡Η\u003C/span>ΒΑΣΙΛΕΙΑΣΟΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>ΕΤΕΛΕΙΩΘΗΣΑΝΜΔΕΚΕ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Μ͡Β\u003C/span>ΡΙΩΚΖ\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>ΙΝ\u003Cspan class=\"intraline\" title=\"line through\">Δ\u003C/span>ΕΚ\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Τ͡Η\u003C/span>Σ⸙\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":209,"html":210},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>",{"id":212,"html":213},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text after Manganaro 2001, with ligatures added\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":215,"html":216},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Tomb of those lying in God at rest, of Constantine, who lived 12 years, of Mellosos, who lived 10 years and of Niketas who lived 8 years. Remember these in your kingdom, O Lord! They died in the month of December on the 27th (day), in the 6th Indiction.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":215,"html":218},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Tomba dei giacenti in Dio qui in pace, di Costantino vissuto anni dodici, di Melloso vissuto anni dieci e di Niceta vissuto anni otto. Di questi ricordati, o Signore, nel tuo regno! Morirono nel mese di dicesmbre (il giorno) ventisette. della indizione sesta.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":220,"html":221},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>  \u003C/p>  ",{"id":223,"html":224},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 51.1378 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscription